# MTLVisibilityResultMode.disabled

**Case**

The result doesn’t contain any data because visibility testing was disabled.

## Declaration

```swift
case disabled
```

## Result modes

- **MTLVisibilityResultMode.boolean**: The result records whether any samples passed depth and stencil tests.
- **MTLVisibilityResultMode.counting**: The result records how many samples passed depth and stencil tests.
